&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Zooming Out at the Viewpoint:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the evening, we visited the spot that offers a fantastic distant view of the Ajanta Caves. The panorama from the viewpoint was the perfect end to our busy day. This place is located at a distance of about 10 km from Ajanta.&lt;/p&gt;

